EmailTemplate.name: Refinance Info email with form
EmailTemplate.subject: Refinancing Your Home with a SunPower Lease - {!Case.Lease__c}
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
IMPORTANT: Do not reply on this email. Please read below carefully.
RE: Lease # {!Case.Lease__c} - HO {!Case.Account}
Thank you for contacting SunPower! We are happy to help you through the process of refinancing your home.
What You Can Expect:
Once we receive the attached document, the team will begin working directly with your lender to handle any issues that might arise pertaining to your SunPower Solar system.
In accordance to your lease agreement, SunPower will be charging a $100.00 documentation fee to your lender. This will be collected and paid once your refinance is completed.
The refinance process usually can be accomplished in about 5 business days depending on the state you live in.
Please provide a copy of the title report, as well as your loan amount with the attached form.
Lets Get Going
To get started with either option, please complete the attached form and return it to us with a copy of your title report via email, phone, or fax:
Email: refinance@sunpower.com
Phone: 800-321-1770
Fax: (512) 684-0288
Please use the subject line: Refinance Request for <Lease number>
We appreciate your business and seek to make this transition as smooth as possible, we cannot process refinance requests on accounts that are more than 30 days past due. Please verify your account is current before submitting your refinance request.
